edge: Timothée Chalamet portrays the character of Paul Atreides in the movie.
Rebecca Ferguson plays the role of Lady Jessica, who is Paul's mother and consort to Leto.
Oscar Isaac enacts the character of Duke Leto Atreides, who is Paul's father and the leader of House Atreides.
Josh Brolin portrays Gurney Halleck, who is the weapons master of House Atreides and one of Paul's mentors.
Stellan Skarsgård appears as Baron Vladimir Harkonnen, who is the leader of House Harkonnen, enemy to House Atreides, and former steward of Arrakis.
Dave Bautista plays the role of Glossu Rabban, who is the nephew of Baron Harkonnen.
Sharon Duncan-Brewster appears as Dr. Liet Kynes, who is the Imperial ecologist and Judge of the Change on Arrakis.
Stephen McKinley Henderson portrays Thufir Hawat, who is the Mentat of House Atreides.
Zendaya appears as Chani, a mysterious young Fremen woman who appears in Paul's visions.
Chang Chen plays the role of Dr. Wellington Yueh, who is a Suk doctor in the employ of House Atreides.
Charlotte Rampling portrays Reverend Mother Mohiam, who is the Emperor's Bene Gesserit Truthsayer.
Jason Momoa appears as Duncan Idaho, who is the swordmaster of House Atreides and one of Paul's mentors.
Javier Bardem portrays Stilgar, who is the leader of the Fremen tribe at Sietch Tabr.
Babs Olusanmokun appears as Jamis, who is a Fremen from Sietch Tabr.
Golda Rosheuvel portrays Shadout Mapes, who is a Fremen working as a housekeeper for House Atreides.
